SUMMARY:Kabbalat Shabbat
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we welcome the Shabbat.  Singing and participation is encouraged in this warm uplifting service\, which is both conservative and egalitarian. The Siddur we use is\, The Song of Abraham\, written by our own Rabbi Mark Bloom.  "A Siddur dedicated to those who wish to increase the meaning and accessibility in traditional Jewish prayer".   For more information see http://www.tbaoakland.org/pages/variety_of_services
