SUMMARY:AM Minyan followed by Breakfast
DESCRIPTION:Our morning minyan meets every Monday and Thursday in the chapel and lasts approximately one hour. We use the older Conservative Siddur (prayerbook) for daily prayer compiled by Rabbi Morris Silverman. This service is always followed by a light breakfast in the social hall lovingly prepared by minyan regulars.
